title: Police Investigate Possible West End Stabbing
text: Police Investigate Possible West End Stabbing Wednesday, September 30, 2015 - 04:45 Updated 13 hours ago Huntington Police are investigating an alleged stabbing that occurred at about 10:40 p.m. Tuesday, Sept. 29 in the 900 block of West Ninth Street in Huntington. A victim reported that she had been stabbed in the back, according to 911 dispatch.
